				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1. ReCon: \"goto 73 -272\"\r\n2. Click on the mushroom ring - this will launch the cinematic\r\n3. ReCon: \"oe und_cine_reset\" -  this will allow to see the cinematic again when clicking on the mushroom ring (by default the game shows it only once)"
				},
